<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Detail Kelas Seni - Relawan Nusantara</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css"> 
    <style>
        /* CSS Tambahan agar langsung terlihat bagus dan dark mode */
        body {
            background-color: #0b0e14;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .detail-container {
            background: #161b22;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .header-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #a855f7; /* Warna ungu biar senada dengan navbar kamu */
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .info-list li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #c9d1d9;
        }
        .info-list li span {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .btn-ambil {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            width: 100%;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-ambil:hover {
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .back-link {
            color: #58a6ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="detail-container">
        <a href="/pendidikan" class="back-link">← Kembali ke Program</a>
        <div class="header-icon">🎨</div>
        <h1>Kelas Seni Kreatif</h1>
        <p>Eksplorasi bakat anak panti asuhan. Wadahi imajinasi mereka lewat lukisan, kriya, dan kerajinan tangan.</p>

        <ul class="info-list">
            <li><span>📅</span> <strong>Jadwal:</strong> Minggu, 10:00 WIB</li>
            <li><span>📍</span> <strong>Lokasi:</strong> Panti Asuhan Kasih</li>
            <li><span>👥</span> <strong>Kuota:</strong> 10 Slot Tersedia</li>
            <li><span>💰</span> <strong>Reward:</strong> 200 Koin</li>
        </ul>

        <button class="btn-ambil" onclick="alert('Misi berhasil diambil!')">Ambil Misi (200 Koin) →</button>
    </div>

</body>
</html>